; Coverage test for format.cc
; Test unrecognized single-letter format character. The format parser
; checks %X against known single-letter mappings (like %D for date,
; %P for payee, etc.) and throws an error for unknown letters.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%Z\n' -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: Unrecognized formatting character: Z
end test
